    <Placemark>
      <name>Marie Antoinette Style Exhibition</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<b>Marie Antoinette Style Exhibition</b><br><i>Arts &amp; Culture</i><br>Sat 20th Sep – Sun 22nd Mar<br>Victoria and Albert Museum, South Kensington<br>Check site<br><br>The V&amp;A hosts the first-ever UK exhibition on the fashionable and ill-fated French queen, Marie Antoinette, exploring her iconic style.<br><br><a href="https://londontheinside.com/whats-on-this-week/">More info / tickets</a>]]></description>
